over at Ripponlea.

01:13:48.320 --> 01:13:50.039
Did you open this one?

01:13:50.040 --> 01:13:52.279
Maybe Mum. She's the one
who kept them for you.

01:13:52.280 --> 01:13:54.719
No, it'll be a big show,
don't you worry.

01:13:54.720 --> 01:13:57.319
We've got an orchestra
at the church.

01:13:57.320 --> 01:13:59.399
(Laughs) That's a bit
over the top, isn't it?

01:13:59.400 --> 01:14:01.479
It's a small chamber
orchestra.

01:14:01.480 --> 01:14:03.639
So, it's a full nuptial,
communion and all?

01:14:03.640 --> 01:14:06.640
- Is she Catholic still?
- It's what your sister wants.

01:14:06.760 --> 01:14:09.079
Best wedding I ever went
to was my friend Morna's.

01:14:09.080 --> 01:14:10.679
It was a simple
exchanging of vows

01:14:10.680 --> 01:14:13.680
in a room full offriends.
It was very moving.

01:14:19.880 --> 01:14:22.319
WOMAN, ON PHONE: It'spart
